The invention discloses a novel bridge circuit with low switching loss, and relates to an electronic circuit technology. Controllable unit of the bridge circuit comprises controllable elements and deflection diodes which are inversely connected in parallel respectively, and are connected with inductive components in series. A deflection diode switching-on current rising velocity control circuit consisting of inductors and resistors is arranged to effectively prevent overquick switching-on current rise from causing the reverse breakdown of the controllable elements and reduce the switching loss of the circuit. The circuit simultaneously effectively clamps over-voltage in switching-off.

